					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ch00bakka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1238719); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1238719&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203534" alt="ch00bakka" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1238719)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ch00bakka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1238719); return false;" >ch00bakka</a></span> <span class="odate time_1536284986 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Sep 2018 01:49</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3960271">
									

<p>Sometimes you start talking shit in IRC and 7 hours later you've got a spicy new tale. ARD wrote most of the tweets, I did the handles and images. The sexy formatting is from TyGently's <a href="/intermission">Intermission</a>, which you should read because it's great.</p>
<p>Secret canon: Jean Cena is an <a href="/scp-3331">scp-3331</a>-1 instance. She's a trans lesbian and a Theatre/Ontokinetics major here to apply her natural Cena reality-bending abilities to the greatest performance art of them all, professional wrestling.</p>
<p>Tweets which didn't quite make the cut:<br />
[2:19pm] ARD: “We imported a poltergeist from Topeka”<br />
[2:21pm] ARD: “Update: the poltergeist had to move back to Topeka. It said that the property taxes on cursed dolls were too high”</p>
<p>[2:39pm] ch00bakka: “hey i’m a freshman, is this sort of thing normal? will this jsut keep happening w different drinks?”<br />
[2:40pm] ARD: “Depends in which house you pledge”<br />
[2:41pm] ARD: “Last year it was Boost - the secret of my energy”<br />
[2:41pm] ARD: .y boost is the secret of my energy<br />
[2:41pm] Gordon: ARD: Boost Is the secret of my energy [old advrt] - length 33s - 33↑4↓ - 9,541 views - Rakesh Mohan on 2012.09.17 - <a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=srIlU93piAI">http://youtube.com/watch?v=srIlU93piAI</a></p>
